  "names": [
    {
      "full_name": "JSC Lantan",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "JSC Lantan is a Russian military-industrial enterprise that develops radar systems which are deployed by the Russian armed forces, including such air defence systems as the Valeria-E electronic intelligence station. Moreover, JSC Lantan is part of the Almaz-Antey concern, a Russian Stateowned arms manufacturer that develops anti-aircraft defence and cruise missile systems for the Russian military. JSC Lantan is therefore supporting materially and benefitting from the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine. Furthermore, JSC Lantan is associated with Almaz Antey, which is supporting materially actions which undermine and threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}